{"tid":777293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家]不滿母親選的旅館太爛　10歲男童持菜刀上街砍人","createTime":"2018-08-12T18:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T12:07:05.000Z","uid":82829,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1f70c919f0d8c6aa44ca0fbdbfedeb209305d8e1","tid":777293,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T18:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201808/0a5f561d88497bf8d50539a98ac55cbd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201808%2F0a5f561d88497bf8d50539a98ac55cbd.JPG&h=c903f697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／翻攝自看看新聞<br />\n<br />\n大陸四川省峨眉市本週四(8日)下午，1名年約10歲的男童手持菜刀，站在馬路中央作勢要砍人，不管在場員警怎麼勸男童都不肯放下菜刀，和幾名員警對峙長達半小時，經警方事後了解，男童是因為母親選的旅館太爛，一怒之下才持刀衝到街上。<br />\n<br />\n根據陸媒報導，當時男童高舉拿著菜刀的右手，一直呈現防禦姿態，在場員警不斷勸導男童放下菜刀，但男童始終充耳不聞，甚至一度提起菜刀作勢要砍人，最後為了防止他做出危險舉動，1名員警脫掉鞋子，悄悄走到男童身後奪刀，隨即將他制伏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201808/53d6f579ea52dac86d6560595488a7e8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201808%2F53d6f579ea52dac86d6560595488a7e8.JPG&h=debf32d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／翻攝自看看新聞<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該名男童和母親到峨眉市玩，當天母親選擇入住1家小旅館，但男童卻希望住得好一點的飯店，於是大吵大鬧後，便拿了1把菜刀衝到街上，不停揮舞似乎想要砍人，但現場目擊者表示，整個過程都未見男童母親出面。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方指出，該名男童和母親事後已被帶到派出所，目前正在接受員警訓誡，同時還必須接受調解。"},{"pid":"e0c1991c8f347a69fc01c04051cd47b6411b5ff1","tid":777293,"uid":33213,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T18:37:50.000Z","msg":"唔怪得菜刀要實名制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1892fe10fd00a99590fb42d7adf03bb7ac5909","tid":777293,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0c1991c8f347a69fc01c04051cd47b6411b5ff1","tid":777293,"uid":33213,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T18:37:50.000Z","msg":"唔怪得菜刀要實名制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:39:43.000Z","msg":"我覺得咁落去真係有需要"},{"pid":"fe4014b9a4af46a6e7407a0bdefb686c203f3cc4","tid":777293,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:06:01.000Z","msg":"地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f667fad53a29c2ee2b27008acb6e34c79c82ba","tid":777293,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"咁好抽"},{"pid":"0c33c1a2142d4a32ea73cc6f788a96a586e243f5","tid":777293,"uid":92690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:14:37.000Z","msg":"好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58782c14bd056af3d8229728b6a1612ee95e3852","tid":777293,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"全個國家都癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd333ca35e1521695266a07df026b5a2b0b7184","tid":777293,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7e50d5b55b64bc11227508462a745638808da0","tid":777293,"uid":195428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T12:01:21.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔斬老母啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a9cfc94c7e5408eb95d69f02682614efa2f2ac","tid":777293,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/31/PaulChun_kill.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20080523051320\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F31%2FPaulChun_kill.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20080523051320&h=a1a8fb53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebc3c30d83baadb48bfc6896e9bf0cd75d78d453","tid":777293,"uid":119347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T12:06:23.000Z","msg":"一槍打死佢咪得囉，搞咁多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5b1a91467912fd67dc245222b12e475b78e29b","tid":777293,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"個老母高招<br />\n扮唔識佢行埋一邊<br />\n等佢無從發洩"}]}